Databricks is the preferred platform due to its robust capabilities, including its foundation on Apache Spark, which allows for efficient processing of large datasets. It supports a collaborative environment where data engineers, data scientists, and business analysts can work together seamlessly. Additionally, its cloud-native flexibility ensures alignment with our IT strategies while offering cost efficiency by consolidating multiple tools into a single platform. This transition will enable us to enhance our data-driven decision-making, optimize operations, and ultimately provide better services to our customers.
